		{
			dependencies: ["6E317C68C5F44D16"]
			description: ["Spartan Weaponry expands physical combat beyond vanilla swords into dedicated fighting disciplines. The Halberd has extended reach and excels against clustered groups. The Greatsword swings in a wide arc. The Katana and Dagger reward attack speed builds. The Lance shines during mounted combat on horseback or Valkyrien Skies vessels. The Javelin is the only throwable. Every weapon type synergizes differently with Mine & Slash's stat soul system — choose your first based on your intended combat style, not material tier. Tinkers and Silent Gear weapons are disabled in this pack; Spartan Weaponry is your physical combat system."]
			id: "391B1915D8FB0F0F"
