		{
			description: ["Iron's Spells & Spellbooks puts spellcasting in the off-hand for the Cloth armor path. Craft the &eIronbound Tome&r yourself at a crafting table — chains, leather, and paper — this quest only completes when you craft it, not when you loot one. The Tome starts with several spell slots; higher-tier books hold more and cast at greater power. Spell Scrolls drop from enemies, mage towers, and dungeon chests — right-click a scroll while holding your Spellbook to inscribe it permanently. Spells cost Mana, which regenerates passively and scales with Intelligence and Wisdom stat soul investment."]
			id: "5976D1DDED910B15"
			rewards: [
				{
