		{
			description: ["Apotheosis overhauls the enchanting table entirely — bookshelves matter by type, not just count. Different shelf types push enchantment power past vanilla's Level 30 cap and gate higher enchantment tier availability. Build your setup with varied shelf types to reach Level 30+ power. A Halberd with Sweeping Edge III + Sharpness V clears rooms; a Katana with Attack Speed + Looting III becomes a stat soul farming machine. Gems from Apotheosis socket into M&S socket slots and stack with your stat soul allocations."]
			id: "52E5DB76B1C28F49"
