		{
			description: ["A different kind of power has entered the world — the way of the ninja. This is a fully optional combat path: pick a clan, learn jutsu, and climb from Genin to Kage entirely outside the pack's main tech and magic progression. Nothing here gates anything else, and nothing else gates this. Open your ninja panel with &eK&r to get started."]
