		{
			dependencies: ["7A7A000000000001"]
			description: ["Your clan determines your starting playstyle — the Uchiha lean into fire and genjutsu, the Hyuga into taijutsu and the Byakugan, the Nara into shadow control. Your village determines which Kage rank you climb toward. Both choices are made from the ninja panel and shape everything that follows."]
